      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I guess... i just don't see much point in a \"next adventure\" anymore. the map feels empty. when you've spent your whole life looking for something and you finally realize it's not coming, the road just starts to feel like a loop you're tired of running. it feels more like a long walk toward a cliff than a journey anymore.",
